bichromate.core

Class sTestOSInformationFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • bichromate.core.sTestOSInformationFactory

  • public class sTestOSInformationFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class Demonstrates sTestOSInformationFactory().
    This class is used to determine the correct file, URI, or URL on a given OS.
    Pass in the file path name, and returns a properly formatted path for the given OS.
    Author:
    davidwramer
